.BR sincosl ()
T}	Thread safety	MT-Safe
.TE
.SH CONFORMING TO
These functions are GNU extensions.
.SH NOTES
To see the performance advantage of
.BR sincos (),
it may be necessary to disable
.BR gcc (1)
built-in optimizations, using flags such as:
.PP
.in +4n
.EX
cc -O \-lm \-fno\-builtin prog.c
.EE
